The paper discusses a classification method for large dimensional data, specifically text datasets and gene expression datasets. This suggests that the paper may belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational linguistics (cs.CL), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV). The use of maximum entropy approach and feature selection further supports the likelihood of the paper belonging to these sub-categories.
